POLICE BRUTALITY; POLICE MISCONDUCT; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- SUITS; LOS ANGELES 
COUNTY SHERIFF'S DEPARTMENT; PRISONS -- LOS ANGELES; PRISONERS -- LOS ANGELES; 
