OFFICIALS -- WAGES AND SALARIES; LOS ANGELES -- GOVERNMENT; GOVERNMENT REFORM; 
POLITICAL CONTRIBUTIONS; LOS ANGELES -- ELECTIONS -- 1990 
</P>
