<TEXT>
<P>
Southwest Conference Commissioner Fred Jacoby denied a protest by Texas, which 
asked that 14 seconds of its Feb. 4 overtime loss to Arkansas be replayed. 
</P>
<P>
The protest was based on officials failing to call a technical foul on Arkansas 
Coach Nolan Richardson, who walked off the court with Texas ahead, 86-83, with 
14 seconds left in regulation. 
</P>
