<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE: NAMES IN THE NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Heisman Trophy winner Andre Ware of the University of Houston won the Davey 
O'Brien national quarterback award. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
