<P>
Photo, . . . and Marketing/And's ads are aimed at helping to make African 
villages self-sufficient. MIKE MULLEN / For The Times; Photo, Prevention 
magazine is selling age-zoned ads; Century 21 is using the Angels, . . . 
</P>
