<P>
PORN QUEEN TRACI LORDS TO WED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Service Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
BALTIMORE 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Traci Lords and Brook Yeaton can say, truly, that theirs is a relationship 
right out of a John Waters movie. 
</P>
<P>
Lords, 21, a one-time teen porn queen, will marry Yeaton, 22, the prop master 
on her latest movie. 
</P>
<P>
The couple met in Baltimore last year while filming the John Waters' movie, 
"Cry-Baby," which is slated for national release April 6. 
</P>
<P>
Lords -- part of an eccentric cast that includes Patty Hearst, Johnny Depp and 
Polly Bergen -- plays a high school virgin in the film. Yeaton also was prop 
master for Waters' last film, "Hairspray." 
</P>
<P>
Lords gained notoriety in 1986 when it was discovered that she had appeared in 
pornographic movies as a minor. She has since been acting in mainstream films. 
